<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạ̉nt sẖkẖṣ mḥbwb</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 (qd kẖlqt ky tṣbḥ .. mḥbwbaⁿạ mn ạllh
 wạlận fy ḥyạtk .. ạ̉nt sẖkẖṣuⁿ mḥbwb)2
 mndẖ ạlạ̉zl .. kạn ḥb ạllh lnạ
 ky ttẖmr ạlmḥbẗ .. ậlạn bynnạ
 km hy ʿẓymẗuⁿ .. bhjẗ ạllh bk
 km nḥn mbthjwn .. bwjwdk wsṭnạ
 (qd kẖlqt ky tṣbḥ .. mḥbwbaⁿạ mn ạllh
 wạlận fy ḥyạtk .. ạ̉nt sẖkẖṣuⁿ mḥbwb)2</lyrics>
